    "content": "Ed Sheeran - You Need Me (Tab is also the same for the Wretch 32 and Devlin Remix)\r\n\r\n\r\nI have a video of this exact tab being played here...\r\n\r\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0Os7aNO2XFs\r\n\r\n\r\nThe song uses all these parts but cuts some bits out in the beginning and end of each verse...\r\n\r\nThey're not worth writing out as I promise you'll pick it up so quickly as opposed to \r\nreading an endless tab.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[Guitar Intro] (Is played on a guitar but what the heck...)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------12--12/14\\12----12/14\\12--|\r\nD|-12h14---------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------|\r\nE|---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Intro]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------3--3--5--5-----------------3--3--5----|\r\nE|-0----3----5----------------0----3----5---------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------------------------3-3---5-5---10\\--|\r\nE|-0--0----0--3-3---3--5-5---5-------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Chorus]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------------------------3-3---3--5-5---10\\--|\r\nE|-0--0----0--3-3---3--5-5---5----------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Ending]\r\n\r\nThis isn't in the song, but I play it on the ending on the video attached just to fill \r\nit out a bit more.\r\n\r\nIf you don't have a 5 string, you can get away with playing all the notes written on the\r\nB string, open on the E string.\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------5---5----5h7-5----|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------7--|\r\nA|---------------------------------------3-3---3----5----------|\r\nE|-------------3x3x3x32323--5x5x5x53535------------------------|\r\nB|-5-5-5-53535-------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------5---5----------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------5h7-5------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------3-3---3----5--------5h7--|\r\nE|-------------3x3x3x32323--5x5x5x53535---------------------------|\r\nB|-5-5-5-53535----------------------------------------------------|[/tab]",
